title.narrative: CHILD PROTECTION AND SOCIAL SERVICES SYSTEMS

description.narrative: New Element, which contributes to Access To Justice, Children With Disabilities, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children (Covid), Social Protection. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2025, national legislative and implementation systems increasingly provide for a protective and caring family environment that enables families and children to demand and benefit from enhanced access to and use of community-based child and family services, quality alternative care, justice system, and protection systems against violence in all environments.
